data.description: Extremely well cared for & renovated 2 bed/2.5 bath townhouse in an highly desirable location, walk to shops/restaurants/markets. Once inside you will fall in love with the tasteful upgrades including but not limited to a beautiful kitchen with recent cabinets and 3cm Cambria Quartz tops / backsplash. The bathrooms have updated vanities, sinks, and quartz tops. The entire living area is LVP with tile in the baths. You will find a spacious living area downstairs, including a built in office nook. This home has an abundance of natural light & all windows are complete with plantation shutters. This home also offers a very nice fenced back yard with a paver patio. Other recent updates in 2018 include: Tile Roof, exterior paint, mailboxes, & water heater.  Some furnishing available for purch Leaseback thru April desired. Listing broker related to seller.
